articles.title: FP3: Verstappen leads Albon and Perez to complete practice clean sweep in Mexico City - Formula 1
articles.description: Max Verstappen completed a practice clean sweep as he set the pace in third and final practice for the Mexico City Grand Prix, fending off the impressive Williams of Alex Albon and his Red Bull team mate Sergio Perez.
